Danny. get off me!

1220
01:23:10.944 --> 01:23:14.989
Sandy. what's the matter with you?
I thought I meant something to you.

1221
01:23:14.990 --> 01:23:16.490
Meant something to you?

1222
01:23:16.491 --> 01:23:19.535
