what people are saying about me?

1297
01:28:17.625 --> 01:28:18.792
Hey.

1298
01:28:22.880 --> 01:28:24.172
Thanks.

1299
01:28:34.559 --> 01:28:36.120
That's the one I was telling you about.

1300
