hubcaps. I lettered in track.

1432
01:41:19.156 --> 01:41:20.531
How do you like that?

1433
01:41:20.532 --> 01:41:23.117
I can't believe it.
Danny Zuko turned jock?

1434
01:41:23.118 --> 01:41:26.329
